But what if it is the bowtruckles who make the...
body:
The general consensus is that bowtruckles live in wanding trees cause *magic*

But what if it is the bowtruckles who make the tree a wanding tree in the first place?

After trying to make two (2) wands on my own I can definitely see the necessity of having something eat the things that eat the wood!

body:
Today’s the big game

The one we’ve been waiting for

We’re ready

We’ll represent the house flag of Gryffindor

We’ve gotta win

The Slytherins have got nothing on us

We’ll defeat them and not even break a sweat

 

Harry and his team swayed, punched the air with their colorful pompoms and did various flips to the delight of the audience, wearing big smiles on their faces as the astonished audience finally recognized the voice and began to scream in joy.

 

Now hear me

Today we meet our destiny

All together

Let’s all march to victory!

(AU - cheerleader!skirt and pom poms!Harry😍)

Inspired: Leading to Victory by DeeDee.

summary: I genuinely offended that people think being mad in behalf of Indonesian because Rowling said Nagini being Indonesian. People...
body:
I genuinely offended that people think being mad in behalf of Indonesian because Rowling said Nagini being Indonesian. People see it as a bad thing when there is myth that can propped this which is good thing. Like people, that’s not how it work when you know shits about Indonesian myths. And Indonesian myths is a lot and very differs based on ethnic and their culture. (Even some Indonesians can be very unaware of their own myths)

Especially when I found out Nagini is from Borneo, Kalimantan. And Rowling refers Naga as race of snake being which fit Batang Garing (Tree of life) Myth (And you all can find it a lot in british journal) that have a race of snake being called Naga from underworld.

The probability she mixed this myth and maledictus is high.

TLDR; Stop being mad for Indonesian’s sake when you don’t bother to know more of it and Indonesians please learn more about our folklore if you cared lol.

P.S also Nagini is basically Naga female version, so it could be not her real name but some kind of name given because she didn’t remember her real name or purposely never tell her real name. An alias if you may.

P.P.S And don’t look for a fight in my post when I just want you all try to see it more beyond your anger and yeap I am Indonesian.

summary: Hi guys! Last time there is no strength for anything. Those who subscribed to me for Steter - forgive me! As soon as I finish...
caption:
Hi guys! Last time there is no strength for anything. Those who subscribed to me for Steter - forgive me! As soon as I finish the quarterly reports, I will start doing Aesthetics again.

And I was so exhausted that I couldn’t bring myself to make normal photos of new bracelets and put them on Etsy. Therefore, I will post here a little preview.
